content:
Can you create a Haiku in JSON format that includes at least one metaphor? Please use the following structure:
{
  "firstLine": {
    "syllables": 5,
    "metaphor": "metaphor1",
    "phrase": "phrase1"
  },
  "secondLine": {
    "syllables": 7,
    "metaphor": "metaphor2",
    "phrase": "phrase2"
  },
  "thirdLine": {
    "syllables": 5,
    "metaphor": "metaphor3",
    "phrase": "phrase3"
  }
}
Remember to include a metaphor in at least one of the lines!

```json
{
  "firstLine": {
    "syllables": 5,
    "metaphor": "whispering breeze",
    "phrase": "Whispering breeze"
  },
  "secondLine": {
    "syllables": 7,
    "metaphor": "painting skies with hues",
    "phrase": "Paints skies with gentle hues"
  },
  "thirdLine": {
    "syllables": 5,
    "metaphor": "silent stars",
    "phrase": "Silent stars listen"
  }
}
```
